{"tid":281122,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)另類聖徒1-2 變相怪傑","createTime":"2017-06-12T13:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T19:00:22.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74a7da6551500002175573b0b8a2a3e06dcdfb0a","tid":281122,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:06:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=oApwOix428vnKSn3%2BW8N74zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ada354d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=oApwOix428vnKSn3%2BW8N74zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=3b9c194d\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=oApwOix428vnKSn3%2BW8N74zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=56a702d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/77/The_Boondock_Saints_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F77%2FThe_Boondock_Saints_poster.jpg&h=ae352bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/6b/The_Boondock_Saints_II_All_Saints_Day_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F6b%2FThe_Boondock_Saints_II_All_Saints_Day_Poster.jpg&h=dea2c7ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/87/The_Mask.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F87%2FThe_Mask.JPG&h=7b0ae89a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.愛爾蘭裔雙胞胎兄弟康納&middot;麥克曼奴和墨菲&middot;麥克曼奴一早參加參加天主教禮拜，中途離開後前去豬肉屠宰場工作，其中墨菲還捉弄了康納一下。後來，兩人與朋友洛克等人在一間酒館慶祝聖派翠克節，從老闆口中得知這間酒館基於俄羅斯黑幫的緣故不得不關店；這時，三名俄羅斯黑幫打手進來要大家離開，兩兄弟嘗試和對方講道理，但反被以暴力回應，使得兄弟倆和客人們與對方打成一團，三位黑幫便因此被麥克曼奴兄弟捉弄一番。第二天一早，兩位俄羅斯黑幫打手闖入兄弟倆家，康納被用手銬綁於馬桶上，而墨菲則被對方帶到樓下巷子準備被槍決；憤怒的康納使勁力地搬起馬桶跑到頂樓將馬桶往下扔，精準地打中一名打手的頭頂，當場死亡，康納也跳下壓倒了另一人便暈了過去，墨菲隨即起身拿馬桶蓋打死被壓倒的那一人，並將對方的槍收走、帶著康納到醫院去..<br />\n<br />\n2.麥克曼奴兄弟康納和墨菲同父親「公爵」挪亞公然在法庭上處死亞卡維塔家族的喬伊老大後，三人於都市消聲匿跡，並定居於愛爾蘭過著安定的生活。八年後，兄弟倆的牧師叔叔希波爾到愛爾蘭通知他們一個神秘的刺客利用兄弟倆慣用的手法來對待被他殺死的牧師，外界稱他們為「處刑人」。這件事很快地鬧開，有些民眾認為是麥克曼奴兄弟做的，但也有人覺得不是他們。康納和墨菲二話不說，馬上修了頭髮和洗澡，並將槍支和舊裝備拿出，隨即前往美國波士頓..<br />\n<br />\n3.史丹利是一個老實本分的銀行職員，經常遭到上司的呵斥，同事的奚落。直到有一天他接待了一個叫做婷娜的金髮美女，史丹利見到她頓時對她頗有好感，然而令史丹利沒有想到的是婷娜竟然是為黑幫頭目多利安搶劫銀行而來打探地形的探子。後來，史丹利受到邀請，與好友一同去市裡的夜總會參加Party，卻又因為沒有地位而被拒之門外，不巧的是還在婷娜面前出盡了洋相，隨後在回家的路上汽車卻又散了架，總之一切倒霉的事全都發生在他身上。但意外的是史丹利無意間獲得了一個外形古怪的面具，失意的他回到家後..<br />\n<br />\n9 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd4c90efa083c3a1abdc4a49ea6aa8fcb55666d","tid":281122,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c951d724c2d9b50407726baa8a1cccb87c083f05","tid":281122,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01879be76cb227cf6bc87c8e162019cb19cb2c57","tid":281122,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy